sequenceDiagram
    participant S as KBMS Server (Audit/Log)
    participant N as Network Layer (Binary)
    participant E as Electron Main (Socket Client)
    participant R as Redux Store (Action)
    participant U as React UI (Toast/Bell)

    S->>N: Phát cảnh báo (Push Event)
    N->>E: Gửi gói tin MessageType.NOTIFICATION
    E->>R: Dispatch addNotification(payload)
    R->>U: Kích hoạt NotificationToasts.tsx
    U->>U: Rung chuông (NotificationBell.tsx)
    Note over S,U: Đảm bảo độ trễ < 10ms trên LAN
